data.description: Look at this 5 bedroom 2 bath beauty that has been completely updated.  Updates include new HVAC, new double pane windows, new sewer line, newer roof, electric, and plumbing.  This gem offers a covered front and back porch, wood privacy fence, all appliances are included, and it is conveniently located.  Don't let this one get away-it will not last long.
